To activate postfix:

- Check the configuration files in ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}
   (see ${EXAMPLEDIR})
- Modify /etc/mailer.conf (see ${EXAMPLEDIR}/mailer.conf)
- Set postfix=YES in /etc/rc.conf

===========================================================================
